                <li style="background-color: black; width: 50px; height: 4px; margin-left: 10px; margin-bottom: -50px; " data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
            </ol>
            <div class="carousel-inner">
                <div class="carousel-item active">

                    <div style="width:300px; height:820px;">
                        <img src="~/image/Android_img1.png" style="margin-left:445px; margin-top:50px; height:600px;" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-md-block">
                        <h5 style="font-size:30px; font-weight:bold; color:black;">병원 정보 실시간 업데이트</h5>
                        <p style="font-size:20px; color:black;">실시간으로 업데이트되는 병원 정보를 확인하세요</p>
