                        <img src="~/image/Android_img2.png" style="margin-left:445px; margin-top:50px; height:600px;" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-md-block">
                        <h5 style="font-size: 30px; font-weight: bold; color: black;">모바일 애플리케이션을 통한 손쉬운 예약 시스템</h5>
                        <p style="font-size: 20px; color: black;">HOSPI앱을 통해 손쉽게 병원 예약을 해보세요</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <div style="width:300px; height:820px;">
                        <img src="~/image/Android_img3.png" style="margin-left:445px; margin-top:50px; height:600px;" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-md-block">
                        <h5 style="font-size: 30px; font-weight: bold; color: black;">병원 진료 내역을 한눈에</h5>
                        <p style="font-size: 20px; color: black;">병원 진료, 처방, 처방받은 약품의 정보를 HOSPI앱을 통해 확인해보세요</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev" style="width:100px">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true" style="filter:invert(100%)"></span>
                <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
            </a>
            <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next" style="width:100px; color:black; ">
